  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/97/97480a181a0732547d159626c2ebe9be.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"\" data-size=\"1382x922\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/97/97480a181a0732547d159626c2ebe9be.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/97/97480a181a0732547d159626c2ebe9be.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/97/97480a181a0732547d159626c2ebe9be.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/97/97480a181a0732547d159626c2ebe9be.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eA new installation at this year’s \u003ca href=\"https://festivaldesarchitecturesvives.com/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eFestival des Architectures Vives\u003c/a\u003e in Montpellier draws attention to food waste through an unexpected medium: stale bread. Titled \u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/merostudios/project/paysage-de-pain\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ePaysage de Pain\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e (Landscape of Bread), by \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/merostudios\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eMERO Studios\u003c/a\u003e, the project uses hundreds of recovered baguettes to form a walkable, sculptural structure within the courtyard of a historic building.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/25/2521699bc1e4ebaaada7199f968de908.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x686\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/25/2521699bc1e4ebaaada7199f968de908.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/25/2521699bc1e4ebaaada7199f968de908.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/25/2521699bc1e4ebaaada7199f968de908.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/25/2521699bc1e4ebaaada7199f968de908.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/85/85809ab2ab0f0af96ea369f84aab8ab6.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x1541\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/85/85809ab2ab0f0af96ea369f84aab8ab6.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/85/85809ab2ab0f0af96ea369f84aab8ab6.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/85/85809ab2ab0f0af96ea369f84aab8ab6.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/85/85809ab2ab0f0af96ea369f84aab8ab6.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe installation responds to a 2018 report by France’s Environment and Energy Management Agency (ADEME), which found that 11% of bakery bread is rejected from sale—of which 60% ends up being destroyed. In collaboration with the local nonprofit Pain Espoir, the baguettes used in \u003cem\u003ePaysage de Pain\u003c/em\u003e were collected and reformed into an architectural system of layered curves and openings.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a2/a20ff67d2adf7ce8cc184a1dbbfec02a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x1541\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a2/a20ff67d2adf7ce8cc184a1dbbfec02a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a2/a20ff67d2adf7ce8cc184a1dbbfec02a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a2/a20ff67d2adf7ce8cc184a1dbbfec02a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a2/a20ff67d2adf7ce8cc184a1dbbfec02a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a8/a89a9d766b091d8bf3c42be984bdb0b2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x1541\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a8/a89a9d766b091d8bf3c42be984bdb0b2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a8/a89a9d766b091d8bf3c42be984bdb0b2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a8/a89a9d766b091d8bf3c42be984bdb0b2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a8/a89a9d766b091d8bf3c42be984bdb0b2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBy inviting visitors to move through and interact with the structure, the installation encourages a reconsideration of waste—not as a byproduct, but as a resource. The project aligns with the festival’s 2025 theme\u0026#34; La Gourmandise,\u0026#34; translating to gluttony, interpreting the concept as a lens for sustainability rather than indulgence.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cbr clear=\"all\"/\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"comments\" id=\"CommentsAnchor\"\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/li\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/ul\u003e\n\t  \t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
